{"tid":289549,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅爆世界Celine小妹好惹負評 麥明詩抱不平：為甚麼不能說句加油？","createTime":"2017-06-19T05:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T15:04:14.000Z","uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42be865f8b8fefdb7fd9d173d9d02ecdf4f1e21e","tid":289549,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"爆紅Celine惹負評 麥明詩抱不平：為甚麼不能說句加油？ <br />\n<br />\n9歲「小巨肺」譚芷昀（Celine）於美國電視選秀節目《全美一叮》演唱名曲《My Heart Will Go On》後爆紅，但遭網民批評她唱歌欠感情，又指她為比賽荒廢學業。「十優港姐」麥明詩路見不平，不禁反問網民「為甚麼不能說句加油？」<br />\n<br />\n　　儘管Celine妹妹的表現令節目的評判和觀眾也拍爛手掌，但畢竟每個人的音樂品味也不盡相同，部分網民指Celine唱歌時「零感情」，「一味靠嗌」，又有人指她小小年紀就發明星夢，荒廢學業。向來敢言的麥明詩就對負評留言表示不解，更在社交網站上貼文為Celine抱不平：「一個九歲嘅香港女仔，可以咁勇敢去踏上舞台，已經好叻好叻。但係見到下面好多留言，『淨係識得嗌』、『唱得毫無感情』、『好普通』&hellip;&hellip;連AGT嘅評判都拍爛手掌，點解我哋唔可以講句加油？」她又在文末加上Hashtag「說好的自己香港自己撐」。"},{"pid":"7ad7586c96389dedaa107ea7f190f922ceacd41a","tid":289549,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 受過教養係唔同d"},{"pid":"33370921eba19c982a0eab821262ef842b9e1085","tid":289549,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"人地寫殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c59f54966b6ad1fdc54f13d1df3f1f84cb6343b","tid":289549,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 受過教養係唔同d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20150613/large/1434191876_36bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20150613%2Flarge%2F1434191876_36bf.jpg&h=b687fe76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e3299b2dc22d668b828d3a17c9707df5b0f7653","tid":289549,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T